    When I run the :exec client command with:
      | pod              | localpd-<%= cb.proj_name %>   |
      | container        | a                             |
      | oc_opts_end      |                               |
      | exec_command     | ls                            |
      | exec_command_arg | -lZ                           |
      | exec_command_arg | /example/hostpath/a/testfilea |
    Then the step should succeed
    And the output should contain:
      | 1000130001 |
