      | pod              | localpd-<%= cb.proj_name %> |
      | container        | a                           |
      | oc_opts_end      |                             |
      | exec_command     | cp                          |
      | exec_command_arg | /hello                      |
      | exec_command_arg | /example/hostpath/a         |
